title: Wall Street Breakfast October 5: U.S. Committee Backs Phased Deployment Of COVID-19 Vaccines
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description:
Our top stories today: U.S. Committee backs phased deployment of COVID-19 vaccines; New York City locking certain areas back down to avert “second wave” of COVID-19; and China pursuing high-risk strategy to rush COVID-19 vaccines to market.
